<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天辛苦你了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聖誕老人託你送給我的禮物，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實是可愛的玩具家具喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或許對聖誕老人來說，<delay8 />
我們都是年幼的小孩子吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我昨天<delay8 />不是收到了<delay8 />
聖誕老人的禮物嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為是你幫聖誕老人送來的，<delay8 />
我就把內容物告訴你吧！<delay frames="30" />
裡面是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />玩具家具喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我當時開心得就像個孩子一樣喔！<delay frames="30" />
<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
謝謝你將禮物送來給我！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
昨天真的很謝謝你！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我送你的禮物<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎麼樣啊？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很可愛吧？<delay frames="30" />
其實我一直都很想送你那個喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明年我們也來<delay8 />
交換禮物吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天能和你交換禮物，<delay8 />
我真的非常開心！<delay20 />謝謝你！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />居然可以交到這麼要好的朋友<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我能生活在<delay8 />這座島上
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你在平安夜裡四處奔波，<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天應該很累吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯～<delay20 />看你的表情<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />似乎沒事！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你昨天<delay8 />不只幫聖誕老人代班，
還跟人交換禮物，<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的很厲害喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧了你，<delay8 />我度過了一個
快樂的平安夜呢！<delay frames="30" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />昨天你幫聖誕老人
送來的禮物……<delay20 />
是很可愛的玩具家具喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再加上昨天跟你進行的交換禮物，<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的平安夜真是太棒了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的很謝謝你！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天的平安夜，你過得怎麼樣啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的話<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />應該還算開心吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我昨晚夢見聖誕老人了喔！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他是位有著白色鬍鬚的紳士<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然沒能見到本尊，<delay8 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是我度過了很棒的平安夜喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>